title: Married At First Sight's Jessika Power suffers an embarrassing wardrobe malfunction
text:
Jessika Power suffered an embarrassing outfit mishap at an event in Melbourne on Sunday.

The 27-year-old former Married At First Sight star stepped out for a Bondi Sands launch in St Kilda.

Dressed in a pale pink miniskirt and matching pale pink blazer with a plunging neckline, Jessika lapped up the limelight.

Bottoms up: Jessika Power (pictured) suffered an embarrassing outfit mishap at an event in Melbourne on Sunday

Propping herself up on the bar counter, Jess appeared oblivious to the fact one of her bottom cheeks was hanging out of her skirt.

Crossing one leg over the other, the former reality star smoldered at the camera as she clutched a drink in one hand.

Her bare bottom sat on the reflective counter top as she showed off her bare legs, accentuated by her nude and clear jewelled stilettos.

Butt of jokes: Propping herself up on the bar counter, Jess appeared oblivious to the fact one of her bottom cheeks was hanging out of her skirt

On the crawl: Despite the daring length of her ensemble, Jessika also posed for photos as she crawled seductively across a brown lounge chair

Despite the daring length of her ensemble, Jessika also posed for photos as she crawled seductively across a brown lounge chair.

She wore her long blonde hair parted in the middle in loose waves, and donned smoky eye makeup and a pink lip.

At one stage, Jess made her way over to where the DJ had set up, and proceeded to dance animatedly from behind the turntables.

Dancing queen: At one stage, Jess made her way over to where the DJ had set up, and proceeded to dance animatedly from behind the turntables

Spinning tracks: After putting on a pair of headphones, Jessika threw one arm up into the air as she danced along with the music

After putting on a pair of headphones, Jessika threw one arm up into the air as she danced along with the music.

She was also seen blowing kisses at the camera as she happily posed for photos at the event.

The limelight loving reality star also posed inside a pale pink arch, which perfectly matched her ensemble.

Think pink: The limelight loving reality star also posed inside a pale pink arch, which perfectly matched her ensemble

Taking the plunge: Dressed in a pale pink miniskirt and matching pale pink blazer with a plunging neckline, Jessika lapped up the limelight

She was seen spinning around as she showed off her candy-coloured outfit from every angle.

And pink power-suits appeared to have been a popular choice for the event, with another guest seen wearing a similar ensemble.

Despite their matching outfits, Jess happily posed alongside her and another guest, who opted for a white dress with eyelets.
description: Jessika Power suffered an embarrassing outfit mishap at an event in Melbourne on Sunday. The 27-year-old former Married At First Sight star stepped out for a Bondi Sands launch in St Kilda.
authors: Demeter Stamell For Daily Mail Australia
